      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for the road? This car is in fair condition and has been a dependable companion, showing some honest wear and character from its journeys. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a solid vehicle at a great price\u2014perfect for someone who values function and value over a showroom shine!",
