    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a solid car that\u2019s ready for your next road trip or just the daily commute, this is the one! Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 29500.0,
